Repo of small stand-alone scripts, probably in py. Useless, useful, personal,testing etc...

Current scripts are:

r_num_2.py - Roman Numeral Converter : Converts 0 to 1,000,000.

/ipanema/plist.py - Port List Game : Guessing game for some well-known ports.

Clean Directory : a better method is bash commands like find.

